    </div>
  </details>

  <details>
    <summary>4. Configuration</summary>
    <div>
      <p>The user can configure their browser at any time to block, restrict, or delete cookies installed on their device. Please note that disabling certain technical cookies may affect the proper functioning of the platform.</p>
    </div>
  </details>
</LegalWrapper>